Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.39,0:01:05.70,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs27\fscx90}穿着衬衫的胸部太过耀眼 我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.64,0:01:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.43,0:01:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.90,0:01:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.08,0:02:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好崇拜她喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.78,0:02:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八神不管做什么都好厉害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.72,0:02:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文武双全,接下来只剩恋爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想谈恋爱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.54,0:02:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正中红心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.41,0:02:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#54 裸体进攻! 五代招架不住的诱惑作战!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此,“心”这部作品是在描述
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于主角的“我”偷跑 超越了友人“K”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:03:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果逼得“K”自杀的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.67,0:03:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这里有什么问题吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.80,0:03:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,八神同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.91,0:03:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假设五代老师是主角“我”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后假设这栋出租公寓的寡妇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.69,0:03:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个二十几岁的绝色美女的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两者间的恋爱关系会成立吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太明白你到底要问什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想问的是 你喜欢那个寡妇吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这跟上课内容有什么关系呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.94,0:03:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要敷衍我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.11,0:03:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道五代老师的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.39,0:03:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在太扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那种小问题弄得手足无措
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.06,0:04:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是搞不懂到底谁才是学生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.63,0:04:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八神同学好像对你很有意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.07,0:04:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管她的外表长得多么成熟 毕竟还是个小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.28,0:04:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论在任何情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能输给你的情欲 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事不用你拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.36,0:04:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么,我会谨记于心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.53,0:04:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,怎么办啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一个礼拜 五代老师就要走了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心,好歹我也是班长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.88,0:04:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他独处的机会,还多得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-再见了 -拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以目前的清扫工作分配 怎么看都很不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.86,0:05:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想出了一个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么班长,接下来麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.74,0:05:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-老师 -哦,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.42,0:05:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先在打扫时分成八组
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后每一组找一个负责人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:06:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女…女校一放学就走光啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.85,0:06:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常都是这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-老师 -什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.43,0:06:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,你们还没走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.74,0:06:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.77,0:06:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.04,0:06:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在讨论新的清扫工作分配 因为我是班长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.31,0:06:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊,早点回去喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,已经讨论完毕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.72,0:06:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下,要是出了什么事 我可不会轻易放过你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.76,0:06:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师,你干嘛逃呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.13,0:06:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.57,0:06:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.70,0:06:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有生气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就在生气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一组的工作内容 都写在这本笔记簿里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,小津江
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.72,0:07:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上完教学实习要回家啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,你最近好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.23,0:07:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你很受欢迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生很喜欢你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.24,0:08:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才怪呢,他们只会消遣我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这很难说喔,表面上故意消遣你 搞不好其实是非常的爱慕你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你呢? 你曾经喜欢过实习老师吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经喜欢一个 很迷人的实习老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.43,0:08:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,马上就忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为两个礼拜转眼间就过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是,转眼间就过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会忘记罗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天回来得好晚喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.31,0:08:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.15,0:08:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:09:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.96,0:09:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟那个叫八神的女孩 后来怎么样了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会问这种事?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么,只是那个年纪的女孩 胆子特别大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想问问看你们的进展如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑,那种小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.05,0:09:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只喜欢年纪大的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.99,0:09:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你能明白就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.06,0:10:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(我喜欢你)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么跟什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,竟敢这样消遣大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.91,0:10:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要以为我不会生气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.21,0:10:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱的激烈告白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都看到了,干嘛藏起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不关你的事!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.96,0:10:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦?叫得那么大声?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代在写爱的交换日记
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借看一下,借看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.41,0:10:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.14,0:10:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看一下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行就是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.64,0:10:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借看一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:11:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛,小气鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.34,0:11:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.78,0:11:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.52,0:11:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.96,0:11:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.53,0:11:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了不该说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.66,0:11:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我一定要拿出老师的威严
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我走了 -路上小…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.97,0:12:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了,惣一郎还没吃饭喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安,有什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.67,0:12:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是五代忘记带去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么样的笔记本呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.07,0:12:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很重要的东西吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.91,0:12:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代也真是粗心大意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.06,0:13:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上是校方的注意事项
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.53,0:13:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有,下午的服装课 改在第三家政教室上课
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外,忘记交家长会费的人 明天一定要带来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.01,0:13:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要找个独处的机会 好好训她一顿才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代老师,五代老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是,有什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.41,0:13:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在问你 有什么事要跟学生们交代的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.12,0:13:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?真的假的?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代在写爱的交换日记?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.60,0:13:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,有问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.71,0:13:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在装什么嘛 你就坦率一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.08,0:13:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以罗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.83,0:14:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,你不是要把五代忘记的 笔记本送去给他吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一之濑太太
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代现在一定很头痛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会吗 也不是什么非送去不可的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.35,0:14:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且笔记本我放在一刻馆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.25,0:14:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 来,请上车
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.32,0:14:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一点,不然学校要放学了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也搭个便车回一刻馆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧,管理员 上车上车
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.43,0:14:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那我走了 -好,你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.71,0:14:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代一定会很高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉,也好,反正很久没回学校去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.26,0:15:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你特地送我来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我向五代问好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.91,0:15:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇,好怀念喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.25,0:16:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,那是五代老师公寓的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寡妇来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是来找五代老师的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.56,0:16:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大胆喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在太厚脸皮了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.71,0:16:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪,不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.94,0:16:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家去了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.61,0:16:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有看到八神同学?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的一点都没变耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.69,0:16:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.43,0:16:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.44,0:17:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗? 怎么特地到学校来?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代忘了带东西 我是送来给他的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-忘了带东西? -是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.52,0:17:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.19,0:17:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊,那就省事多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.39,0:17:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对五代老师究竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.67,0:17:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.99,0:18:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,既然她要用 年纪大的从容对付我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就利用年轻的本钱 把她解决掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.27,0:18:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直找不到两人独处的机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.51,0:18:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师,快来快来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.55,0:18:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-请快点来 -跟我们来,快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之跟我们来就对了,快啊快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面有奇怪的声音?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来没有什么异常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.91,0:18:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们干什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.41,0:18:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开门!快开门啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.45,0:18:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八神,你穿这样要干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.60,0:19:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静点,要不然我要大叫喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.07,0:19:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,突然来打扰您
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好多年不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师一点都没变 吓了我一大跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.21,0:19:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊,千草你才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.88,0:19:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,抱歉,应该是音无才对 以前叫习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.62,0:19:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到五代是你的房客啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他老师当得还顺利吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好 只是有一些学生非常爱慕他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住…住手,八神 不要再闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被别人看到的话 下场会很严重的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.81,0:19:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下场会很严重的是老师你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:20:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是为了想困扰老师 才做这种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很困扰,非常困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.75,0:20:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.69,0:20:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八神,你听我说 要好好的爱惜自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.22,0:20:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老掉牙的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.96,0:20:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.39,0:20:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惨了,是老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.03,0:20:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.87,0:20:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空要再来玩喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业以后,大家都很少回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.57,0:20:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道还有学生在里面?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再闹了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.86,0:20:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我就那么没有魅力吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:20:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么要逃避我?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.51,0:21:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我有喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.95,0:21:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个公寓的寡妇对不对?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.88,0:21:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧,五代老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有必要跟你说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要敷衍我!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.69,0:21:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.53,0:21:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.03,0:21:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我话还没说完
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.23,0:21:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.42,0:21:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 你要让他们闹到什么时候?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.99,0:21:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心看到出神了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.49,0:21:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.90,0:21:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.70,0:22:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.20,0:22:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上荻老师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.04,0:22:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听我说,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.77,0:22:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管…管理员…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,没有被当作色狼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.26,0:22:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然罗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,幸好我有自制
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.98,0:22:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-五代 -是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.88,0:22:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肚子饿不饿?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.65,0:22:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.89,0:22:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找个地方吃点东西再回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.96,0:22:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.49,0:22:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我请客
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.66,0:23:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么好意思,我请客啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.43,0:23:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-没关系 -不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.39,0:23:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,你一定要让我请
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.40,0:23:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.46,0:23:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天真的很想请你吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.67,0:23:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让你请了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.94,0:23:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们通通给我听好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.17,0:23:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算抱着恶作剧好玩的心态 但是男生会突然产生冲动的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们平常的言行举止 一定要有高中生的自觉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是八神同学你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.11,0:23:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是,我已经深切反省了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好,毕竟你是个班长
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.65,0:23:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而班长应该更要以身作则 做全班的榜样才对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.89,0:23:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会为了这点小事就气馁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.09,0:23:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.97,0:23:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!你要在这里过夜?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.33,0:23:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.30,0:23:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想干什么?快把衣服穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.87,0:23:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.37,0:23:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.91,0:23:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‘睡衣女孩突击! 一刻馆爱情大混乱’
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.51,0:24:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员,这下该怎么办呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.04,0:24:02.04,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.79,0:24:29.89,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx94}两人坐在黎明的护栏上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.22,0:24:43.36,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx94}至今一直在寻找遗落爱的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.77,0:24:55.25,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx94}为什么… 现在… 你… 一阵风…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.53,0:25:02.59,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx94}目光交会… 只有… 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.62,0:25:09.26,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx94}为什么… 现在… 我… 在雨中…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.29,0:25:18.98,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx94}忽然… 胸口… 梦… 濡湿而发光

